er; padding:0 14px; font-size:12px; color:#a59986; max-width:240px;\">🔍&nbsp; Ask a question…<\u002Fdiv>\n          <div style=\"margin-top:14px; display:flex; gap:8px;\">\n            <div style=\"background:#211C17; border-radius:10px; width:54px; height:36px;\"><\u002Fdiv>\n            <div style=\"background:#fbe3d1; border-radius:10px; width:54px; height:36px;\"><\u002Fdiv>\n            <div style=\"background:#ece7f7; border-radius:10px; width:54px; height:36px;\"><\u002Fdiv>\n          <\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n        <!-- content -->\n        <div style=\"padding:32px 34px;\">\n          <div style=\"display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px;\">\n            <div style=\"background:#fbe3d1; color:#c8611a; border-radius:20px; padding:4px 12px; font-family:'Space Mono',monospace; font-size:11px; font-weight:700;\">INTERACTIVE PORTAL<\u002Fdiv>\n            <div style=\"font-family:'Space Mono',monospace; font-size:11px; color:#a59986;\">01<\u002Fdiv>\n          <\u002Fdiv>\n          <div style=\"font-family:'Unbounded',sans-serif; font-weight:700; font-size:26px; letter-spacing:-.01em; margin-top:14px;\">Compass — the ethics hub<\u002Fdiv>\n          <div style=\"margin-top:16px; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:11px;\">\n            <div><span style=\"font-family:'Space Mono',monospace; font-size:11px; font-weight:700; color:#E2701A;\">CHALLENGE&nbsp;&nbsp;<\u002Fspan><span style=\"font-size:14.5px; color:#5b5247; line-height:1.5;\">Employees couldn’t find policies — so they guessed, or skipped them.<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n            <div><span style=\"font-family:'Space Mono',monospace; font-size:11px; font-weight:700; color:#E2701A;\">APPROACH&nbsp;&nbsp;<\u002Fspan><span style=\"font-size:14.5px; color:#5b5247; line-height:1.5;\">A searchable hub with plain-language policy pages, a Speak Up flow, and a decision guide for gray areas.<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n            <div><span style=\"font-family:'Space Mono',monospace; font-size:11px; font-weight:700; color:#E2701A;\">OUTCOME&nbsp;&nbsp;<\u002Fspan><span style=\"font-size:14.5px; color:#5b5247; line-height:1.5;\">One home for ethics that meets people at the exact moment of doubt.<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n          <\u002Fdiv>\n          <div style=\"margin-top:20px; display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:8px; font-weight:700; font-size:14px; color:#E2701A;\">Open the live prototype →<\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n    <\u002Fa>\n\n    <!-- PROJECT 2: TRAINING -->\n    <a href=\"#/Training Module.dc\" style=\"display:block; background:#fff; border:1px solid #ece0cc; border-radius:24px; overflow:hidden; box-shadow:0 8px 28px rgba(120,80,30,.07); color:#211C17;\">\n      <div style=\"display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1.05fr;\">\n        <div style=\"background:#211C17; padding:34px; display:flex; flex-direction:column; justify-content:center; min-height:300px; color:#FBF6EE; position:relative; overflow:hidden;\">\n          <div style=\"position:absolute; right:-40px; bottom:-40px; width:150px; height:150px; border-radius:50%; background:#6B4FB0; opacity:.25;\"><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div style=\"font-family:'Space Mono',monospace; font-size:11px; color:#E2701A; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:.08em;\">MODULE 02 · 4 MIN<\u002Fdiv>\n          <div style=\"font-family:'Unbounded',sans-serif; font-weight:700; font-size:28px; line-height:1.05; margin-top:12px;\">Conflicts of Interest<\u002Fdiv>\n          <div style=\"margin-top:18px; height:8px; background:#3a332d; border-radius:6px; overflow:hidden; max-width:240px;\"><div style=\"width:62%; height:100%; background:#E2701A;\"><\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div style=\"margin-top:18px; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:8px; max-width:250px;\">\n            <div style=\"background:#2a2521; border:1px solid #3a332d; border-radius:10px; padding:9px 12px; font-size:12px; color:#c2bbb2;\">Recuse yourself — and say why.<\u002Fdiv>\n            <div style=\"background:rgba(111,181,138,.14); border:1px solid #2f6044; border-radius:10px; padding:9px 12px; font-size:12px; color:#9fd6b6;\">✓ Nice call<\u002Fdiv>\n          <\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n        <div style=\"padding:32px 34px;\">\n          <div style=\"display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px;\">\n            <div style=\"background:#ece7f7; color:#6B4FB0; border-radius:20px; padding:4px 12px; font-family:'Space Mono',monospace; font-size:11px; font-weight:700;\">INTERACTIVE TRAINING<\u002Fdiv>\n            <div style=\"font-family:'Space Mono',monospace; font-size:11px; color:#a59986;\">02<\u002Fdiv>\n          <\u002Fdiv>\n          <div style=\"font-family:'Unbounded',sans-serif; font-weight:700; font-size:26px; letter-spacing:-.01em; margin-top:14px;\">A microlearning module<\u002Fdiv>\n          <div style=\"margin-top:16px; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:11px;\">\n            <div><span style=\"font-family:'Space Mono',monospace; font-size:11px; font-weight:700; color:#6B4FB0;\">CHALLENGE&nbsp;&nbsp;<\u002Fspan><span style=\"font-size:14.5px; color:#5b5247; line-height:1.5;\">Annual ethics training was a 40-slide click-through nobody retained.<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n            <div><span style=\"font-family:'Space Mono',monospace; font-size:11px; font-weight:700; color:#6B4FB0;\">APPROACH&nbsp;&nbsp;<\u002Fspan><span style=\"font-size:14.5px; color:#5b5247; line-height:1.5;\">A 4-minute branching module: teach, then a real scenario and a knowledge check with instant feedback.<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n            <div><span style=\"font-family:'Space Mono',monospace; font-size:11px; font-weight:700; color:#6B4FB0;\">OUTCOME&nbsp;&nbsp;<\u002Fspan><span style=\"font-size:14.5px; color:#5b5247; line-height:1.5;\">Learners practice the actual decision — not just read about it.<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n          <\u002Fdiv>\n          <div style=\"margin-top:20px; display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:8px; font-weight:700; font-size:14px; color:#6B4FB0;\">Take the module →<\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n    <\u002Fa>\n\n    <!-- PROJECT 3: EXPLAINER -->\n    <a href=\"#/Animated Explainer.dc\" style=\"display:block; background:#fff; border:1px solid #ece0cc; border-radius:24px; overflow:hidden; box-shadow:0 8px 28px rgba(120,80,30,.07); color:#211C17;\">\n      <div style=\"display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1.05fr;\">\n        <div style=\"background:#1b1714; padding:34px; display:flex; flex-direction:column; justify-content:center; align-items:center; text-align:center; min-height:300px; color:#FBF6EE; position:relative; overflow:hidden;\">\n          <div style=\"position:absolute; right:-70px; bottom:-80px; width:220px; height:220px; border-radius:50%; border:24px solid #E2701A; opacity:.10;\"><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div style=\"font-family:'Space Mono',monospace; font-size:11px; color:#E2701A; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:.12em;\">A 60-SECOND BRIEF<\u002Fdiv>\n          <div style=\"font-family:'Unbounded',sans-serif; font-weight:800; font-size:30px; line-height:1.02; letter-spacing:-.02em; margin-top:12px;\">When in doubt,<br><span style=\"color:#E2701A;\">disclose.<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div style=\"margin-top:20px; width:52px; height:52px; border-radius:50%; background:#E2701A; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; color:#fff; font-size:16px;\">▶<\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n        <div style=\"padding:32px 34px;\">\n          <div style=\"display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px;\">\n            <div style=\"background:#e4efe8; color:#2f6044; border-radius:20px; padding:4px 12px; font-family:'Space Mono',monospace; font-size:11px; font-weight:700;\">MOTION / EXPLAINER<\u002Fdiv>\n            <div style=\"font-family:'Space Mono',monospace; font-size:11px; color:#a59986;\">03<\u002Fdiv>\n          <\u002Fdiv>\n          <div style=\"font-family:'Unbounded',sans-serif; font-weight:700; font-size:26px; letter-spacing:-.01em; margin-top:14px;\">A 60-second explainer<\u002Fdiv>\n          <div style=\"margin-top:16px; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:11px;\">\n            <div><span style=\"font-family:'Space Mono',monospace; font-size:11px; font-weight:700; color:#2f6044;\">CHALLENGE&nbsp;&nbsp;<\u002Fspan><span style=\"font-size:14.5px; color:#5b5247; line-height:1.5;\">Some topics need to land before anyone opens a handbook.<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n            <div><span style=\"font-family:'Space Mono',monospace; font-size:11px; font-weight:700; color:#2f6044;\">APPROACH&nbsp;&nbsp;<\u002Fspan><span style=\"font-size:14.5px; color:#5b5247; line-height:1.5;\">Wrote and designed a kinetic explainer that delivers the core idea in under a minute.<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n            <div><span style=\"font-family:'Space Mono',monospace; font-size:11px; font-weight:700; color:#2f6044;\">OUTCOME&nbsp;&nbsp;<\u002Fspan><span style=\"font-size:14.5px; color:#5b5247; line-height:1.5;\">A shareable asset for onboarding, Slack, or a screen in the break room.<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n          <\u002Fdiv>\n          <div style=\"margin-top:20px; display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:8px; font-weight:700; font-size:14px; color:#2f6044;\">Watch it →<\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n    <\u002Fa>\n  <\u002Fdiv>\n\n  <!-- APPROACH -->\n  <div id=\"approach\" style=\"background:#211C17; color:#FBF6EE; margin-top:56px;\">\n    <div style=\"max-width:1080px; margin:0 auto; padding:60px 28px;\">\n      <div style=\"font-family:'Space Mono',monospace; font-size:13px; font-weight:700; color:#E2701A; letter-spacing:.06em;\">HOW I WORK<\u002Fdiv>\n      <div style=\"font-family:'Unbounded',sans-serif; font-weight:700; font-size:32px; letter-spacing:-.02em; margin-top:8px; max-width:680px;\">Translate the rule into something human.<\u002Fdiv>\n      <div style=\"margin-top:30px; display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr); gap:18px;\">\n        <div style=\"background:#2a2521; border-radius:16px; padding:22px;\"><div style=\"font-family:'Space Mono',monospace; color:#E2701A; font-weight:700;\">01<\u002Fdiv><div style=\"font-family:'Unbounded',sans-serif; font-weight:600; font-size:17px; margin-top:10px;\">Listen<\u002Fdiv><div style=\"font-size:13.5px; color:#b6ada2; margin-top:6px; line-height:1.5;\">Sit with the policy team and the people who’ll actually use it.<\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n        <div style=\"background:#2a2521; border-radius:16px; padding:22px;\"><div style=\"font-family:'Space Mono',monospace; color:#E2701A; font-weight:700;\">02<\u002Fdiv><div style=\"font-family:'Unbounded',sans-serif; font-weight:600; font-size:17px; margin-top:10px;\">Translate<\u002Fdiv><div style=\"font-size:13.5px; color:#b6ada2; margin-top:6px; line-height:1.5;\">Rewrite the legalese into plain language people trust.<\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n        <div style=\"background:#2a2521; border-radius:16px; padding:22px;\"><div style=\"font-family:'Space Mono',monospace; color:#E2701A; font-weight:700;\">03<\u002Fdiv><div style=\"font-family:'Unbounded',sans-serif; font-weight:600; font-size:17px; margin-top:10px;\">Design<\u002Fdiv><div style=\"font-size:13.5px; color:#b6ada2; margin-top:6px; line-height:1.5;\">Shape it into the right format — page, module, or motion.<\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n        <div style=\"background:#2a2521; border-radius:16px; padding:22px;\"><div style=\"font-family:'Space Mono',monospace; color:#E2701A; font-weight:700;\">04<\u002Fdiv><div style=\"font-family:'Unbounded',sans-serif; font-weight:600; font-size:17px; margin-top:10px;\">Measure<\u002Fdiv><div style=\"font-size:13.5px; color:#b6ada2; margin-top:6px; line-height:1.5;\">Watch completion and questions — then tighten it.<\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n\n      <div style=\"margin-top:34px; display:flex; gap:10px; flex-wrap:wrap;\">\n        <div style=\"border:1px solid #3a332d; border-radius:30px; padding:8px 16px; font-size:13px; color:#d8d1c8;\">Plain-language writing<\u002Fdiv>\n        <div style=\"border:1px solid #3a332d; border-radius:30px; padding:8px 16px; font-size:13px; color:#d8d1c8;\">Instructional design<\u002Fdiv>\n        <div style=\"border:1px solid #3a332d; border-radius:30px; padding:8px 16px; font-size:13px; color:#d8d1c8;\">Information architecture<\u002Fdiv>\n        <div style=\"border:1px solid #3a332d; border-radius:30px; padding:8px 16px; font-size:13px; color:#d8d1c8;\">Internal systems &amp; databases<\u002Fdiv>\n        <div style=\"border:1px solid #3a332d; border-radius:30px; padding:8px 16px; font-size:13px; color:#d8d1c8;\">Brand &amp; motion<\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n    <\u002Fdiv>\n  <\u002Fdiv>\n\n  <!-- FOOTER CTA -->\n  <div style=\"max-width:1080px; margin:0 auto; padding:60px 28px 70px; text-align:center;\">\n    <div style=\"font-family:'Unbounded',sans-serif; font-weight:800; font-size:40px; letter-spacing:-.03em;\">Let’s make compliance<br><span style=\"color:#E2701A;\">worth reading.<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n    <div style=\"margin-top:26px; display:flex; gap:13px; justify-content:center; flex-wrap:wrap;\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/taylor-wolpe/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:8px; background:#E2701A; color:#fff; padding:15px 30px; border-radius:30px; font-weight:700; font-size:15px;\">Connect on LinkedIn →<\u002Fa>\n    <\u002Fdiv>\n    <div style=\"margin-top:40px; font-family:'Space Mono',monospace; font-size:11.5px; color:#a59986; line-height:1.6; max-width:680px; margin-left:auto; margin-right:auto;\">All work shown is a self-initiated concept built around “Brindle Beverage Co.,” an invented brand created solely to demonstrate craft. It is not a real company, product, or affiliation, and contains no confidential or employer material.<\u002Fdiv>\n  <\u002Fdiv>\n\n<\u002Fdiv>\n\n\n\n<\u002Fx-dc>\n\n\n<\u002Fbody><\u002Fhtml>","Compass Portal.dc":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html><head>\n<meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n<